 1.很想出國留學 但實在好像有夠貴一年就要100多萬台幣(是嗎?) 
Not necessarily, I know schools in the US charge as low as $600,000 per school year for tuition and living expenses. 

2.而我是高職生 讀完三年 如果要出國讀書 要讀一般的大學? 還是像台灣一樣有科技大學? 
It doesn't matter what type of college. It matters whether the college has the major you want. 

3.然後交換學生又是什麼?? 其實我不太懂[留學and交換生的區別是?] 
Exchange students must go to that particular school and come back to your original scool. 留學you go where you want to and stay at your will. 

4.聽說讀觀光的會去瑞士留學 ((那邊好像不是講英文...? 
Switzerland is famous for hotel management. They speak English, German, and French. 

5.不然請問還有哪裡是比較便宜的? ((偏向歐美 
There are many schools that have hotel management and tourism majors in the US. 

6.出國留學是四年都要念完 然後交換生可以分幾年 ((對不對?)) Wrong. 

我覺得我不想要只待在一個小地方 我想出去看看 而且我想要訓練自己 Very good thinking. Go see the world and you have a chance to have a world view. 

但是 不知道家人肯不肯 之前海外遊學他們肯 不過最後沒人陪我去就沒去了 You don't need anyone to accompany you. You must grow up by challenging yourself constantly. You can't live with your family all your life, can you?





